reviewText: Having traveled to many places in France, this was a very good overview.  I recommend it to anyone who is a first time traveler and even a seasoned Francophile who wants a quick review of some of the best places to visit in France.
Planning a trip to Europe Summer '14 and wanted some ideas of things to see.  This was very helpful and showed places that I want to visit that I had never before heard about.
This video is very differentt from other tour videos. It introduces many lovely and cute french towns. It shows beautiful buildings and castles. Love it.
